Title: JET Range Automatic Air Vent Check Valve 3/8 x 1/2"
Description: This JET Range automatic air vent with 3/8 x 1/2" threaded connections is designed with a vacuum break to prevent air locks. A central heating safety device, the air vent releases built up air. As water flows through the system, a float opens or closes the vent depending on the water level. When the system is full the float is pushed to the top, closing the vent until the water level drops.

Title: Honeywell Home V4043H1056 Home Twin Pack Zone Valve 22 mm
Description: Suitable for any number of flow control applications, the Honeywell Home V4043H motorised two port zone valve with 22mm compression connections can be used in domestic or light commercial central heating systems. It is designed to be positioned where it won't block a vent or cold feed when closed, and can be plumbed at any angle provided the powerhead isn't below the horizontal level of pipework. V4043H can be fitted into a confined space, however ventilation should be available in order to maintain the valve's ambient temperature range. Access should also be reserved for removal of the valve's powerhead where needed.
